174
00:13:23,219 --> 00:13:24,971
Napísala mi dlhý list.

175
00:13:25,055 --> 00:13:26,431
Zmente vetu iným slovom.

176
00:13:27,307 --> 00:13:28,224
Pán Nakamura.

177
