234
00:19:12,777 --> 00:19:13,653
Zasa?

235
00:19:14,070 --> 00:19:15,447
Čo si zač?

236
00:19:15,989 --> 00:19:17,824
Som HiME.

237
00:19:18,033 --> 00:19:19,034
HiME?

